Who: SCOURGE, Rat Trap, Quickstride (Not sure if Darkhawk is here or not)
Location: Black Fortress - Just outside

> Scourge and Darkhawk start to do Guard"
>
> "YEs, sir "said DarkHawk and Perceptor and they started to do their dotuies

Scourge nodded, "On it." he said as he quickly made for the door,
obviously uncomfortable with all the intrigue.

As he walked toward the door he saw the trio of soldiers making their
way to the throne room. Part of him wanted to accompany them, but his
orders still stood. With a slight shrug he walked outside the
fortress, shifted shape and began to patrol from the air.

However it was only a moment before he picked up at least two Maximal
energy signatures and he began to bank in their direction.

(TAG)

Preston
